ath? Breathe naturally don’t manipulate the most natural thing there’s ever been in life", "timestamp": 1775109498}, {"author": "kookie78", "author_id": "10144705", "id": "18087252665213658", "text": "Wow this is wild", "timestamp": 1775099397}, {"author": "pjf7772", "author_id": "72107537651", "id": "18100893857479298", "text": "I’ve been doing Wim Hof  breathing method for over two years truly is life-changing!", "timestamp": 1775094100}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612537602_1792347638120631_8245360874967659388_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE8fu2qyzgKlvQzaQP_VgVnrNZy5Ec8eFkBoRcJYFLMoQ4_EZ43ttBO75o2xmwxNM4&_nc_ohc=iu7gHje2Q14Q7kNvwEzILoO&_nc_gid=FO_99ULgGcbEaWqDrWsqMg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af33yqoSqdXUcduJxTgKe_QIaH4_1bXWHWBwT133RIU2LA&oe=69D4DD7C&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612537602_1792347638120631_8245360874967659388_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE8fu2qyzgKlvQzaQP_VgVnrNZy5Ec8eFkBoRcJYFLMoQ4_EZ43ttBO75o2xmwxNM4&_nc_ohc=iu7gHje2Q14Q7kNvwEzILoO&_nc_gid=FO_99ULgGcbEaWqDrWsqMg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af33yqoSqdXUcduJxTgKe_QIaH4_1bXWHWBwT133RIU2LA&oe=69D4DD7C&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612537602_1792347638120631_8245360874967659388_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE8fu2qyzgKlvQ